Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是恋爱咨询吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:53.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我也不知道怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:58.97,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord4\fs75\pos(1402,890)}辉夜大小姐想做到底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,听说学生会也能做这类咨询
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:59.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有辉夜大小姐能帮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:01.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:06.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,倾听同学烦恼也是学生会的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会长也总把这挂在嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:12.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 是怎样的恋爱烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道能和男朋友圆满分手的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:19.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:23.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是两三阶段之前的咨询呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:27.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,关于有男朋友的女生的咨询
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.85,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜大小姐您这么受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.42,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有丰富的恋爱知识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:33.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还如此沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:36.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有恋爱经验的我怎么可能回答得出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.21,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,您一定能给我非常合适的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:39.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对我的期待也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:45.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而作为四宫一族的人一言既出驷马难追
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只能想办法渡过难关了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你想要分手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:53.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为他突然对我告白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我就顺势答应他了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:03:00.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我其实并不了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道要怎么对待他才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:05.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说比交往前隔阂还深
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很对不起他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:11.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会分手了反而更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:16.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在交往前你们完全是陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你会有这样的感觉也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不是讨厌他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:26.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:31.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也不知道这到底算不算是爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:36.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 从发现他的优点开始如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:37.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,找到喜欢他的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:41.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 无论是谁都会有优点或是惹人喜爱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:49.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说 他做事认真 成绩优异 努力上进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:53.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,或是十分善良 从不抛弃有困难的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者是眼神比较凶恶之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神凶恶不是缺点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:04.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢 他在意自己眼神凶恶这点就可爱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您喜欢眼神凶恶的男生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才说的你都忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要说辉夜大小姐身边眼神凶恶的人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事 我们继续谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:20.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,发现他的优点 从一个优点喜欢上他开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会发现他有很多长处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:26.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,等回过神来你就无法从他身上移开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果每天都盯着他看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就会慢慢喜欢上他本人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友是这么跟我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是我说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:37.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶居然不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:42.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是刚才说的那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,事情我大概了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:47.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不让我一起加入恋爱话题实在太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:55.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这种话题请交给本人「恋爱侦探千花」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么气喘吁吁的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我更早前就已经在这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但又跑去戏剧部一趟换了身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你对无法明白对他的想法而感到烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:10.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那名为「恋爱」的遗失品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我这个名侦探来帮你找到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:22.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 请想象一下那个男生与别的女生亲热的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,总之就先想象一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:34.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,气愤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,换而言之那就是所谓「嫉妒」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:48.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为喜欢他才会觉得不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,越是觉得不舒服就越是爱得深沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:55.46,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,Love？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.94,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:59.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我认为柏木同学是喜欢你的男朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:02.63,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能对会长抱有这样的感情 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只要慢慢培养这份感情就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:03.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:07.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为自己是无法喜欢上向我告白的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样冷酷无情的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:11.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:15.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我一定是喜欢着他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉已经快得出结论了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:24.18,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么样才能更自然地跟男朋友聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:24.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要给出一些合适的建议才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「认知平衡」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:31.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以试试利用「罗密欧与朱丽叶效应」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.09,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,罗密欧与朱丽叶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,罗密欧与朱丽叶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,罗密欧与朱丽叶的爱情受到阻挠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为共同面对强大的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们爱得更深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,强大的敌人是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不一定是人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有共同的假想敌就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可没有这样的假想敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:57.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 每个人都有不得不面对的强大敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个社会本身！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:05.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,社会？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,永不停止的战争 永不消除的贫富差距
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这更强大的敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:12.37,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,诶等等 应该是测试或者烦恼之类的小事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:17.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 只要二人齐心反抗这腐败的社会就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:18.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,规模太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:22.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了 我们这就去做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:24.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊我说 你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:30.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吗 我们真的没有创造出新的反社会分子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:39.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家帮帮忙筹款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.93,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家帮帮忙筹款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.82,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩原本就对慈善活动有兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎成了不错的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,祈愿和平的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:57.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这才是真正意义上的反抗社会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她的男朋友是来找会长咨询过的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:10.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:13.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会长会参加这个活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 因为我接到校外筹款活动的申请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:24.79,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家帮帮忙筹款
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.24,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:25.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 我看他们既不是一时兴起也不像是在打发时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.13,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家帮帮忙筹款
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.46,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看着虽然没经验但努力的他们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:32.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然力量微薄但不知不觉想帮他们一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:38.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这种活动根本不适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:43.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你的这点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日战局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:48.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜的败北
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.97,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H484447&\fs70\b0\pos(1905,15)\fad(200,0)}请\N大\N家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.97,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H484447&\fs70\b0\pos(1845,15)\fad(200,0)}帮\N帮\N忙\N筹\N款
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.97,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H484447&\fs70\b0\pos(1785,15)\fad(200,0)}拜\N托\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:56.80,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord4\fs85\pos(446,902)}白银御行想耍耍威风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就差一点点！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,运动白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:17.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银虽然非常擅长学习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:21.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而关于运动方面真的是毁灭级别的不擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,长年的送报纸 暑假的搬家打工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:29.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就连每天骑15公里单车上学都轻松完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:33.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银御行绝不是身体素质不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:38.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而是令人绝望地不擅长体育运动 这就是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他要继续保持他在秀知院学园的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:44.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就需要持之以恒地训练
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:47.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下周有排球课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须得达到普通人的级别才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,请你认真点行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:58.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 那个像快死一样的羊驼的是会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:58.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个快死一样的羊驼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:04.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么怎样都不顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没问…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原书记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了东西在这儿 就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:22.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,被看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个蠢得不行的动作被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:31.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,文武双全 万事精通的白银会长的招牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:36.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明明啥都没干但是什么都会的我这一印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,考前复习？没怎么做过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:40.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,球真好玩儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哎随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么看我我也不太受伤就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:52.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下次不是会有排球课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:55.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为能借到体育馆 所以我在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不太擅长发球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话我来教你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:07.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊 要教别人首先你自己得会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我区区排球还是会打的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:14.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,多么利落的发球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得咋样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:22.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没想到你会有这样的绝技
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:28.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我来教你 你肯定一下就上手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:34.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 请人教你的时候要用什么态度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,请 请你教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:42.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就先来找找问题出在哪儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,请你发几次球给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:49.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:52.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:54.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯——？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:03.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:08.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不管打几次都会打到自己的头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太注意自己的头的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又抓不住时机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:14.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,完全陷入僵局了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:19.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 打球的时候要把眼睛睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是呀 就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次把眼睛睁大再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样怎么可能有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有睁眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有睁开眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛摆出一副
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「按你说的做了 但还是不行」的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 一毫米都没睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:47.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:51.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这就是传说中的易普症
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:57.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是会长自己的想法和动作不协调
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,先从跳的时候睁眼开始练习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要彻底改正过来 做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.89,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H393737&\3c&HF5F4F2&\b1}魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:12.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3 4 5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.68,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,556 557 558 559
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:18.49,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,984 985 986
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,跳的时候不要闭眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:22.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,从早到晚特训三天后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.23,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,球是最好的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:26.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经和普通人的差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:36.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,已经比动物进化很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:37.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我还可以继续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么能这么努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:47.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想被她看见弱小的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:50.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她要看 就要让她看见帅气的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:59.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人 是会长喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:01.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白…才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:02.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你个恋爱脑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你就别遮遮掩掩了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:05.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,谁呀 是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:06.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,做…做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,终于做到了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:24.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原书记 多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那 藤原书记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来请教我怎么垫球和接球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子是我培养的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:09.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日战局 白银和藤原的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银选手这次表现很好。
